Tawiah weputara onwe ya EP N'ime ime ime Jodi (Bush Girl Records) na Recreate na Lima Limo Records
N'afọ 2019, o wepụtara album mpụta mbụ ya Starts Again na First Word Records
Na 2018, o mere njem na Moses Sumney Recreate na na 2020 na-amalite ọzọ na Michael Kiwanuka.
Tawiah arụwokwa ọrụ na ndị na-ese ihe gụnyere Blood Orange, Kindness, Mark Ronson, Cee-Lo, Kano, Wiley, Ghostpoet, Zed Bias na Eric Lau
N'oge na-adịbeghị anya, ọ na-ede ma na-eme egwu ọhụrụ nke Cinematic Orchestra "Wait for Now".

Ọrụ ya enwetala otuto na mkpuchi sitere na OkayPlayer, The Fader, Afropunk, The Guardian, iD Magazine, Complex, Stylist, Refinery, London na Stereo, Bandcamp na Time Out, ịkpọ aha ole na ole, na nkwanye ùgwù onwe onye abịarutela ebe niile
afọ ndị ahụ, site na Quincy Jones ruo Adele, Jeff Goldblum na Queen Latifah
